object.script: -- Author: Toastery -- GitHub: https://github.com/Toast732 -- Workshop: -- -- Developed & Minimized using LifeBoatAPI - Stormworks Lua plugin for VSCode -- https://code.visualstudio.com/download (search "Stormworks Lua with LifeboatAPI" extension) -- By Nameous Changey -- Minimized Size: 1041 (1355) chars Z=true Y=false X=property W=math V=input U=output.setBool T=V.getNumber S=W.atan R=X.getNumber Q=X.getBool b=0 c=0 d=0 e=0 f=Q("Requires Is Occupied?")g=Q("Radar Rotation")h=R("Time Between Missiles (s)")i=R("Min Mass")j=R("Max Mass")k=R("Min Y")l=R("Max Y")m=R("Min Distance")n=R("Max Distance")o=R("Radar FOV X")*.75 p=R("Radar FOV Y")*.75 if g then local q=p p=o o=q end r=W.pi*2 function s(t,u,v,w)return S(t-v,u-w)/r end function x(v,w,t,u)return W.sqrt((t-v)^2+(u-w)^2)end function onTick()local y=Y b=b+1 d=0 e=0 z=Y A=Y B=V.getBool(1)if not f or f and B then C=T(8)if j==0 and i==0 or j==0 and i>=0 and C>=i or C>=i and C<=j then D=T(5)E=T(7)F=T(1)G=T(3)H=x(D,E,F,G)if H>=m and H<=n then I=-T(4)J=s(F,G,D,E)if W.abs(J-I)<=o then K=T(6)L=T(2)if S((L-K)/H)/r-T(9)<=p then if c==0 or b-c>=h*60 then U(1,Z)y=Z end end end end end end if not y then U(1,Y)end end function W.M(N,min,max)return max<N and max or min>N and min or N end function O(N)return N~=N and 0 or N end function P(N,min,max)return(N-min)/(max-min)%1*(max-min)+min end

object.script:
-- Simple EPN, by Lassi#9944
lastRateX=0 lastRateY=0 lastAccX=0 lastAccY=0
navRate=property.getNumber("Rate nav") navAcc=property.getNumber("Acc nav") navJerk=property.getNumber("Jerk nav")
smoothclosingv=0
function onTick() rateX=input.getNumber(1) rateY=input.getNumber(2) closingv=-input.getNumber(3) distance=input.getNumber(4) --smoothclosingv=smoothclosingv+(closingv-smoothclosingv)/2 smoothclosingv=closingv Tgo=math.min(distance/math.max(closingv*60,1),10)
accX=rateX-lastRateX accY=rateY-lastRateY jerkX=accX-lastAccX jerkY=accY-lastAccY
if accX==rateX then accX=0 end if accY==rateY then accY=0 end if jerkX==jerkX then jerkX=0 end if jerkY==jerkY then jerkY=0 end
Mg=7/math.max(math.min(Tgo,10),7) Mc=math.max(math.min(Tgo-5,5),0)/5 * 8
output.setNumber(1,(rateX*navRate*math.abs(smoothclosingv) + accX*navAcc*Tgo^2 + jerkX*navJerk*Tgo)*property.getNumber("Yaw multiplier")*Mg+input.getNumber(5)*Mc) output.setNumber(2,(rateY*navRate*math.abs(smoothclosingv) + accY*navAcc*Tgo^2 + jerkY*navJerk*Tgo)*property.getNumber("Pitch multiplier")*Mg+property.getNumber("Pitch trim")+input.getNumber(6)*Mc)
output.setNumber(3,rateX) output.setNumber(4,rateY) output.setNumber(5,closingv) output.setNumber(6,smoothclosingv)
lastRateX=rateX lastRateY=rateY lastAccX=accX lastAccY=accY end

tab={} function onTick() value=input.getNumber(1) if value ~= 0 and math.abs(value) < 100 then table.insert(tab,value) end total=0 for i,v in ipairs(tab) do total=total+v end total=total/#tab if #tab>8 then table.remove(tab,1) end
if #tab==0 then total=0 end
output.setNumber(1, total) output.setNumber(2, input.getNumber(2)) end

object.script:
types = {"R80D","R30D","RM95","nTGP","PJ2k","RPOD","CANO","FUEL","Misc","Bast","R80E","GBU","ASM","AAM","AShM","Ltrp","LM4+","R80X","RKT","65","9","7","120","L131","IRIS","Mete","Torp","Bomb"} guidetypes = {"RADAR","LASER","DUMB","OTHER"} guide = "" minr = "" maxr = ""
function onTick() t = input.getNumber(1) gt = input.getNumber(2) guide = guidetypes[gt] or "" minr = math.floor(input.getNumber(3)) maxr = math.floor(input.getNumber(4)) if property.getText("Custom name (override default text output)") ~= "" and property.getText("Custom name (override default text output)") then typ = property.getText("Custom name (override default text output)") else typ = types[t] end typnum1 = string.byte(typ or "",1) output.setNumber(5,typnum1) typnum2 = string.byte(typ or "",2) output.setNumber(6,typnum2) typnum3 = string.byte(typ or "",3) output.setNumber(7,typnum3) typnum4 = string.byte(typ or "",4) output.setNumber(8,typnum4) text = (string.char(typnum1 or 0) .. string.char(typnum2 or 0) .. string.char(typnum3 or 0) .. string.char(typnum4 or 0)) end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawText(1,1,text) screen.drawText(1,13,guide) screen.drawText(1,19,minr) screen.drawText(1,25,maxr) end

tab={} v=0 smooth=0 function onTick() value = input.getNumber(1)
table.insert(tab,value) if #tab>60 then table.remove(tab,1) end smooth=0 for i,v in pairs(tab) do smooth=smooth+v end smooth=smooth/#tab
output.setNumber(1,smooth) end
